0.118 g
50. 742. Td
(Glidepath requires individual user authentication \(email/password\) and records all actions with operating) Tj
T* (initials and Zulu timestamps, providing equivalent accountability. However, it does not currently integrate) Tj
T* (CAC authentication for automated digital signatures. CAC integration requires DoD identity infrastructure) Tj
T* (not available on the current commercial hosting platform. A Platform One Party Bus onboarding request) Tj
T* (has been submitted to enable CAC authentication in a future release.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.118 g
50. 668.75 Td
(A pre-drafted DAF Form 679 waiver request is available in the project documentation. T-3 waivers require) Tj
T* (Wing/CC approval per DAFMAN 90-161, Table A10.1.) Tj
ET
