0. G
BT
/F2 18 Tf
20.6999999999999993 TL
0.118 g
50. 742. Td
(Why Identified Gaps Do Not Require Waivers) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.118 g
50. 711.2999999999999545 Td
(The compliance matrix identifies 35 GAPs across all chapters. None of these trigger a waiver for the) Tj
T* (following reasons:) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 13 Tf
14.9499999999999993 TL
0.118 g
50. 672. Td
(1. Procedural Items ó Manual Entry Sufficient) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.118 g
50. 649.0499999999999545 Td
(Several AF Form 3616 annotation items \(Para 2.5.2.10.5\) are marked as GAPs because Glidepath does) Tj
T* (not auto-generate entries for them \(e.g., personnel on airfield, SOF calls, CMAVs, weather warnings,) Tj
T* (equipment malfunctions, ARFF capability\). However, users can manually enter any of these events in the) Tj
T* (Events Log at any time. The app does not prevent compliance ó it simply does not automate every entry) Tj
T* (type. No format deviation means no waiver is required.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 13 Tf
14.9499999999999993 TL
0.118 g
50. 573.7999999999999545 Td
(2. Training Program \(Chapter 8 ó 14 GAPs\)) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.118 g
50. 550.8500000000000227 Td
(Chapter 8 requirements are for the NAMT to maintain training records, master task lists, and evaluation) Tj
T* (documentation. Until Glidepath is designated as the official training record system, these requirements) Tj
T* (are fulfilled by whatever system the unit currently uses \(paper, TBA, Excel\). The planned Training) Tj
T* (Management Module would serve as an "electronic training record format equivalent" once built ó also) Tj
T* (without requiring a waiver.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 13 Tf
14.9499999999999993 TL
0.118 g
50. 475.6000000000000227 Td
(3. External System Integrations) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.118 g
50. 452.6500000000000341 Td
(DAFMAN does not require all functions to reside in a single system. NOTAM Manager, AFRIMS, CE work) Tj
T* (order systems, and other external tools continue to operate independently. Glidepath supplements ó not) Tj
T* (replaces ó these systems. No waiver is needed for the absence of direct integrations.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 13 Tf
14.9499999999999993 TL
0.118 g
50. 402.7000000000000455 Td
(4. Physical and Organizational Requirements) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.118 g
50. 379.7500000000000568 Td
(Requirements for staffing levels \(Ch 3\), facilities and equipment \(Ch 4\), and physical inspection conduct) Tj
T* (\(vehicle with emergency equipment, etc.\) cannot be fulfilled by software and are outside application) Tj
T* (scope. These are marked N/A and do not require waivers.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 18 Tf
20.6999999999999993 TL
0.118 g
50. 323.8000000000000682 Td
(Compliance Summary) Tj
